						<p>Mutilated stone in the hillock near the village.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">[Vikrama-chōḻa] ••• •••••</hi></p>						

						<p>Fragmentary. Begins with the king's <hi rend="italic">praśasti, pūmādu-puṇara,</hi></p>						

						<p>It seems to record a gift of land, Mentions [A]ṇḍappūr among the boundaries.</p>						

